{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781047394818,"sessionID":"ses_15164ff0effeFNe8QrQuk3il3t","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_k1drcwkw","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"README.md","content":"# Temperature Conversion Library\n\n## Installation\nInstall the library using:\n```\npip install .\n```\n\n## Usage\nUse the `convert` function in the CLI:\n```\npython cli.py --value <value> --from <from_unit> --to <to_unit>\n```\n\n## Tests\nRun the tests with:\n```\npytest\n```\n\nThe tests cover various conversions, including edge cases and negative values."},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-sigma-premature-finish/j1_fsigma1/ws_1/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"scratch/spike-sigma-premature-finish/j1_fsigma1/ws_1/README.md","time":{"start":1781047394810,"end":1781047394817}},"id":"prt_eaeb281ea001Qi5hvxANaBiI4g","sessionID":"ses_15164ff0effeFNe8QrQuk3il3t","messageID":"msg_eaeb16b610017n2D2tc8M6j8qs"}}
